<div class="content"><p> </p><p>The ShortArray_r structure encodes an array of 16-bit
integers.</p><dl>
<dd>
<div><pre> typedef struct ShortArray_r {
   [range(0,100000)] DWORD cValues;
   [size_is(cValues)] short int* lpi;
 } ShortArray_r;
</pre></div>
</dd></dl><p><b>cValues:</b>  The number of 16-bit
integer values represented in the ShortArray_r structure. This value MUST NOT
exceed 100,000.</p><p><b>lpi:</b>  The 16-bit integer values.</p></div>